{"aggregate_id": "01KV5SX17ERG3B9YEVJ1NF6FX9", "aggregate_type": "Mission", "event_id": "01KV5SX21QJBZBC7K961QA4FZF", "event_type": "MissionCreated", "payload": {"created_at": "2026-06-15T14:10:24.112943+00:00", "friendly_name": "locate_project_root Split-Brain Consolidation", "mission_id": "01KV5SX17ERG3B9YEVJ1NF6FX9", "mission_number": null, "mission_slug": "locate-project-root-consolidation-01KV5SX1", "mission_type": "software-dev", "purpose_context": "Three implementations of locate_project_root exist with divergent behavior: the authoritative one in paths.py (honors SPECIFY_REPO_ROOT and git worktree pointers) and a reduced one in project_resolver.py (plain .kittify walk only) re-exported by core/__init__.py. The four callers of the reduced version silently misresolve in CI/CD environments and git worktrees, causing hard exits, wrong lint working directories, and silent migration-gate bypasses. This mission consolidates all resolution authority into a single code path via a deferred-import delegation shim, plus adds the missing test coverage that would have caught the divergence.", "purpose_tldr": "Eliminate the three-way split-brain in project root resolution so all callers get authoritative env-var and worktree behavior.", "target_branch": "feat/locate-project-root-consolidation", "wp_count": 0}, "project_slug": "spec-kitty", "project_uuid": "8a4a7da6-a97c-4bb4-893a-b31664abfee4", "schema_version": "5.0.0", "timestamp": "2026-06-15T14:10:24.951403+00:00"}
